# Backtest harness — track manifests, ignore bulky historical data.
#
# - cohorts/  : cohort manifest JSON files (committed — schema definitions).
# - data/     : JSONL caches of historical prices/financials downloaded
#               by Chunk 4 fixture builders. Bulky and reproducible — do
#               NOT commit. Small hand-crafted fixtures used by unit
#               tests are explicitly allow-listed below.

data/*
!data/benchmark-prices-fixture.jsonl
